# Agent Harness Entrypoint

This repository is a metarepo for standardizing team AI workflows.

Before non-trivial work, read `agent-kit/AGENTS.md`. It is the canonical agent entrypoint for this framework.

Detailed rules live in `agent-kit/agent-rules/`. Document skeletons live in `agent-kit/skeletons/`.

Do not duplicate the kit rules in Cursor rules. If the workflow changes, update the canonical files under `agent-kit/` and keep this plugin rule as a pointer.
